OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early low cloud, mist and
OL,6,Ffog clearing through the morning to
OL,7,Fleave a dry, mild and bright afternoon
OL,8,Fon Thursday with plenty of hazy
OL,9,Fsunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry and fine through Thursday
OL,12,Fevening and remaining largely clear
OL,13,Fovernight into Friday with cloud
OL,14,Fslowly thickening and the odd mist or
OL,15,Ffog patch possible.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FRemaining mild but becoming
OL,18,Fcloudier through the morning on
OL,19,FFriday, with light rain turning
OL,20,Fheavier and more persistent into the
OL,21,Fafternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
